value.def: Mongolian means belonging or relating to Mongolia, or to its people, language, or culture.
value.tran: 蒙古国的;蒙古国人的;蒙古语的;蒙古国文化的

value.def: A Mongolian is a Mongolian citizen, or a person of Mongolian origin.
Mongolian is the language that is spoken in Mongolia.

example.ex: Until August of this year there was no complete translation of the New Testament in Mongolian.
example.tran: 直到今年8月，还没有《新约全书》的蒙古语全译本。
